{
  "texts": [
    "We utilize 3 ReRAM tiers and 1 systolic array tier, each with 16 cores placed in a 4 x 4 grid as shown in Fig. 2.",
    "TSV interconnect is utilized to connect planar tiers with 48 vertical links.",
    "Additionally, the bottom tier (systolic array) and the top tier (ReRAM) are connected point-to-point through 16 TSV links to support long-range communication.",
    "We maintain a consistent aspect ratio for all TSV links including skip links.",
    "Hence, for skip links, we need to increase TSV diameter."
  ]
}